cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CC 

The paper deals with the problem of predicting binary sequences with limited assumptions about the sequence. This problem is related to information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also proposes a variant of the forecasting problem, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
